Package: MRTSampleSizeBinary
Type: Package
Title: Sample Size Calculator for MRT with Binary Outcomes
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Eliot Wong-Toi, Thabat Dahdoul, Tianchen Qian
Maintainer: Tianchen Qian <t.qian@uci.edu>
Description: Provides a sample size calculator for micro-randomized trials (MRTs) with binary outcomes based on methodology developed in Qian et al. (2020) <doi:10.1093/biomet/asaa070>. Also provides a power calculator when the sample size is input by the user.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
